The paper deals with dynamic epistemic logic, which is a subfield of logic and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves the analysis of topological properties, which suggests that it could be relevant to cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) and cs.MS (Mathematical Physics). Finally, the paper deals with dynamical systems, which could make it relevant to cs.SY (Systems and Control).
